subject: College Athletics
Volleyball
NCAA Volleyball Championships
Colleges and Universities
lead_paragraph: The 12th-seeded Seminoles, the Cinderella story of the N.C.A.A. tournament, meet ninth-seeded U.C.L.A. on Thursday for the right to play in the national championship match.
